<h2 id="实现命令队列" class="heading-element"><span>3 实现命令队列</span>
  <a href="#%e5%ae%9e%e7%8e%b0%e5%91%bd%e4%bb%a4%e9%98%9f%e5%88%97" class="heading-mark">
